267
00:12:22,980 --> 00:12:24,337
Say good-bye to these!

268
00:12:24,420 --> 00:12:26,134
Those are blue, too!

269
00:12:26,359 --> 00:12:27,901
There were blue hand prints on them?

270
00:12:28,007 --> 00:12:30,590
Yes, and I swear to you they weren't...

271
00:12:30,660 --> 00:12:33,184
Yours. No, I know. It all points to Dad.

272
00:12:33,287 --> 00:12:35,652
Dad's in Reno, Kitty's in Reno... Dad's in Kitty.

273
00:12:35,744 --> 00:12:37,736
He must be a Blue Man. I'm gonna go check out the theater.

274
00:12:37,813 --> 00:12:39,789
Okay. I'll meet you there.

275
00:12:40,696 --> 00:12:44,336
I just have to break down the salad bar and set up the leather pony.

276
00:12:44,423 --> 00:12:45,632
What's the leather pony?

277
00:12:45,718 --> 00:12:47,500
I don't know. We don't have that at lunch.

278
00:12:49,092 --> 00:12:51,924
So Michael called Lindsay to say he'd found her husband.

279
00:12:51,996 --> 00:12:53,788
All right, I'm on my way.

280
00:12:53,906 --> 00:12:55,796
I'll just bring him back with me.

281
00:12:56,598 --> 00:12:58,073
He wants to come home?

282
00:12:58,176 --> 00:12:59,679
I mean, against his will.

283
00:12:59,794 --> 00:13:02,225
Well, knock him out, if you have to. He's my husband.

284
00:13:02,333 --> 00:13:05,103
Just watch the kids like you promised, okay?

285
00:13:05,994 --> 00:13:07,243
- I'm not...
- Neither am I.

286
00:13:07,575 --> 00:13:08,651
Hold it.

287
00:13:09,306 --> 00:13:14,026
And the kids found themselves closer than ever on the bumpy road to Reno.

288
00:13:14,831 --> 00:13:15,527
Hello?

289
00:13:15,625 --> 00:13:17,211
Lindsay, uh, hey, hi.

290
00:13:17,239 --> 00:13:20,048
Michael said not to call you, but I... I missed you so much.

291
00:13:20,146 --> 00:13:21,733
You miss me?

292
00:13:22,130 --> 00:13:24,206
