- Nothing.

293
00:13:24,258 --> 00:13:27,446
I was driving out there, but this is crazy. We have to be realistic.

294
00:13:27,508 --> 00:13:30,032
No, no, but the thing is, I can't leave Kitty.

295
00:13:30,119 --> 00:13:33,340
I just... what with all the sexual intercourse and whatnot.

296
00:13:33,448 --> 00:13:35,041
You bastard!

297
00:13:35,208 --> 00:13:37,180
- What are you doing!?
- Nothing!

298
00:13:37,283 --> 00:13:41,292
I will be backstage after the Blue Man show, whether Kitty likes it or not.

299
00:13:41,368 --> 00:13:42,873
Sounds good. One quick question, though.

300
00:13:42,955 --> 00:13:48,157
What if Kitty's not there and I'm less of a Blue Man and more of a... cocktail waitress?

301
00:13:48,322 --> 00:13:50,152
- She's turning again!
- Hang up! Hang up!

302
00:13:50,190 --> 00:13:51,911
I'll see you there. Thank you, bye.

303
00:13:51,998 --> 00:13:54,783
Michael was already at the theater looking for George Sr.,

304
00:13:54,864 --> 00:13:57,421
