- No.

414
00:19:13,353 --> 00:19:15,779
Oh. Then of course I'm going to like it.

415
00:19:15,887 --> 00:19:17,489
I, I, I like Ann.

416
00:19:17,628 --> 00:19:23,214
No. It... It's just, it's a problem without an answer.

