420
00:19:33,212 --> 00:19:34,222
Yeah, I guess so.

421
00:19:34,309 --> 00:19:35,383
I know so.

422
00:19:35,482 --> 00:19:38,319
So, here's the plan. Tomorrow morning, we're gonna get up early.

423
00:19:38,426 --> 00:19:41,482
Before we tell the cops that Pop Up escaped from prison,

424
00:19:41,560 --> 00:19:44,099
we're going to go down to the lake, we're gonna discuss your girl problem,

425
00:19:44,170 --> 00:19:45,493
and it's going to be fun.

426
00:19:45,554 --> 00:19:47,170
Especially the part with the cops.

427
00:19:47,672 --> 00:19:51,775
All right? Whatever your problem is with the girl, we're going to figure it out.

428
00:19:51,831 --> 00:19:53,427
That's what this place is for.

429
00:19:54,043 --> 00:19:55,855
That, and cheating on Gangee.

430
00:19:56,162 --> 00:19:57,969
You know, I'm really glad you brought me here, Dad.

431
00:19:58,077 --> 00:19:59,736
Yeah, we needed this.

432
00:20:00,007 --> 00:20:02,987
And this time, I'm not gonna let the family drag me away.

433
00:20:03,780 --> 00:20:07,968
And the next morning, Michael rose early to spend the day with his son...

434
00:20:08,511 --> 00:20:12,864
