435
00:20:14,277 --> 00:20:16,642
Dad! What the hell are you doing?

436
00:20:16,734 --> 00:20:21,424
Sorry, I can't let you let Oscar out of prison, or they'll come for me!

437
00:20:21,583 --> 00:20:24,470
Hey, how do you like the cabin?

438
00:20:30,794 --> 00:20:33,165
On the next... Arrested Development...

439
00:20:33,247 --> 00:20:35,307
Lucille arrives at the cabin.

440
00:20:35,745 --> 00:20:37,983
( bleep ) me. There's no cabin.

