00:20:50,895 --> 00:20:51,868
Yeah, me, too.

447
00:20:51,971 --> 00:20:52,804
...her cousin.

448
00:20:52,903 --> 00:20:54,001
Want to make out?

449
00:20:54,139 --> 00:20:55,426
Yeah, sure, why not?

450
00:20:56,348 --> 00:20:58,791
